"{\"uid\": \"thenationonlineng.net-best-medal-hope-amusan-eyes-olympics-medal-at-third-attempt\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sports  August 8, 2024 byTunde Liadi  World Record Holder in the 100m hurdles,Tobi Amusanis thrilled to have an explosive start in the event's heat and she's eyeing an Olympic medal at the third time of asking at the Paris 2024 Games.Amusan topped her Heat in a time of 12.49 seconds, ahead of America's Alaysha Johnson (12.61 seconds), and Jamaica's Janeek Brown (12.84 seconds) and she thereafter expressed her satisfaction with her performance and her optimism for the remaining races ahead.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 82, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obito_Uchiha\", \"score\": 0.9999576375051757, \"rank\": 3.8087953995992734e-05, \"text\": \"Tobi\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obito_Uchiha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Obito_Uchiha\"}, {\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9909767556073732, \"rank\": 0.006776672586252299, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999883297756461, \"rank\": 1.1668859507136714e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janeek_Brown\", \"score\": 0.9999999999479314, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janeek Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janeek_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janeek_Brown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt strong and confident out there today,\\\" Amusan told Making of Champions.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Winning the heat with such a time gives me a great boost going into the semifinals.\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Reflecting on her journey, Amusan added: \\\"The first time I came as an Olympian, I was like 18/19, the second time I think I was a little bit experienced and I did not get on the podium, this time I think, it's my season.Related NewsTinubu congratulates Gumel, Amusan on international featsResilient\\u00a0\\u00a0Amusan\\u00a0\\u00a0proud of\\u00a0\\u00a0'golden'\\u00a0\\u00a0silver at Tokyo 2025Okowa salutes Amusan on silver medal feat at World ChampionshipsRead Also:FIFA lifts transfer ban on Kastina United\\\"God is great, my third Olympics, the goal is to come out here and execute each round, I think I did a pretty decent job.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999998881322, \"rank\": 1.1191142916104188e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gumel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gumel\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gumel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gumel\"}, {\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.5852615612904708, \"rank\": 0.7086365271423555, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\"